column5: So happy to have a newborn this small on camera! 1st of 2010 for me!! :D:D Even saw its tiny prints on the dirt path on the way out      Caught a doe about to burst a few weeks ago. This would maybe be the same doe above!      Nice plum belly on this one maybe another Doe with a baby
Funny how they know the camera is there!
Nice pics. Cute ones the first two.
My camera is about 6 inches in height by 4 inches wide. Sooo tiny yet they see it. Maybe the red light that flashes catches their eye.
